  every 4px at very low opacity (0.012). This adds a faint film-grain/CRT
  texture that makes the header feel cinematic without any image assets.
  pointer-events: none ensures it doesn't interfere with clicks.

  Gradient text on .title-reel — -webkit-background-clip: text clips a
  red-to-crimson gradient to the letter shapes. drop-shadow adds a red halo. The
   background-clip approach gives far richer color than a flat color value.

